  "detailed_description": "Featuring a movement system that's as unforgiving as it is addictive, your gaming skills will be put to the ultimate test! Dive into the absurd world of Jeff, a turtle with human legs on a mission to find his father.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054670/extras/72e03ab3d34ec23c4bc7672306061cda.avif?t=1727744248\" width=616 height=137 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054670/extras/7837f38d5a9cfb0e13f453e3483206d4.poster.avif?t=1727744248\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054670/extras/7837f38d5a9cfb0e13f453e3483206d4.webm?t=1727744248\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054670/extras/7837f38d5a9cfb0e13f453e3483206d4.mp4?t=1727744248\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Difficult Movement</strong>: Speed is the key to success here, the faster you move the further you jump. Time your jump with your speed to land where you need to go, or don't, whatever works best for you!</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054670/extras/7209e6669e303de82a0775aae8e904b6.avif?t=1727744248\" width=616 height=137 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054670/extras/cd73767abe292c9395620e96eec952e8.poster.avif?t=1727744248\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054670/extras/cd73767abe292c9395620e96eec952e8.webm?t=1727744248\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054670/extras/cd73767abe292c9395620e96eec952e8.mp4?t=1727744248\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Challenging World</strong>: Since Jeff is a tiny turtle, even the smallest of obstacles are massive deals for him! Guide him through treacherous sands, moss, snow, and even space! </li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054670/extras/d3d39dd15e45845447fff4e337333f1b.avif?t=1727744248\" width=616 height=137 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054670/extras/ae59cc596e0f680cce8bacc931e2db17.poster.avif?t=1727744248\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054670/extras/ae59cc596e0f680cce8bacc931e2db17.webm?t=1727744248\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054670/extras/ae59cc596e0f680cce8bacc931e2db17.mp4?t=1727744248\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Unique Protagonist</strong>: Guide Jeff, our quirky turtle with massive human quads, through a series of mind-bending obstacles and laugh-out-loud moments. </li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054670/extras/5c2a92903a9ad98e66c457226f1526ab.avif?t=1727744248\" width=616 height=137 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054670/extras/dc4fcdacde7003e36137f81e35a37416.poster.avif?t=1727744248\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054670/extras/dc4fcdacde7003e36137f81e35a37416.webm?t=1727744248\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054670/extras/dc4fcdacde7003e36137f81e35a37416.mp4?t=1727744248\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Funny Moments</strong>: Spend hours attempting, and failing the same jump! I promise you, someone will find it funny hearing you scream at your computer screen!</li></ul><br>Get ready to rage, laugh, and cry as you navigate Jeff through a journey that's difficult to play but impossible to put down.<br><br>Are You Up for the Challenge?",
